parameters:
\SE\SE[2]In other words, I am from the same village as you
all.... \!\SE[3]I escaped from the village together with
Melissa and Lunoa, but I got separated along the
way...\!\SE\SE[2]And now, I have finally arrived.

\SE[2]Currently, it seems like I am working as a maid at the
residence of the nobleman Donyoku in Caudine.
\SE[3]Therefore, I shouldn't have any problems concerning
life-threatening situations or food, clothing, and shelter.
\SE[6]If that's the case, then... that's good to hear...

\SE[47]I've been searching for you all this time, but I
never expected you to be so far away...

\SE[74]I see... But I'm glad to hear that you all are safe.
\SE[7]What kind of person was she?

\SE[21]Um... \SE[12]First and foremost, her breasts are
huge. You should definitely take a look at them once...
\SE[20]That's what I heard.

\SE[11]No... I mean, they're really, really huge.
\SE[14]She's even hanging a sign like I picked them from my
own garden!... \SE[56]It's impossible not to notice...
they're that big...
\SE[92]I-Is it really necessary to go that far...?
\SE[52]No, it's strange to introduce her from there...

\SE[14]Well, what the...!! \!\SE[12]Are you saying that
those aren't huge...!?

\SE[57]No... Regarding that... \SE[38]... It was my bad.
That was definitely huge.

\SE\SE[4]We've only been talking about breasts...
\!\SE[3]But, um, Nikita? You're a noble's maid, right?
\!\SE[4]If that's the case, then I think that's fine too...
\SE[38]However, I can't say that for sure...

\SE[2]It's not confirmed information, so I can't assert it,
but \SE[48]that noble, Duke Donyoku, has many bad rumors
surrounding him.

\SE[2]Duke Donyoku... I've never heard of him. \SE[3]I
thought I was aware of influential nobles.

\SE[2]After the death of King Cordin, he cleverly made money
with foreign currency and became a nouveau riche noble.
\SE[3]It seems that he is not very interested in overt
diplomacy.

\SE\SE[38]Regarding that Donyoku Duke... \!\SE[47]It seems
that he gathers women without any family ties to live as he
pleases... \!\SE[38]If they go against him, they will be
cast aside...

\SE[12]No way... So, you're saying... \SE[14]That means
she's going through something terrible...!?

\SE[74]...So, what would you do in that case? \!\SE[3]Even
if it's considered impure, we shouldn't forcibly take her
away. \.On the surface, we're just employing her normally.

\SE[74]And here's another piece of unconfirmed information!
\SE[10]Actually, there are suspicions of tax evasion
surrounding Duke Donyoku. \SE[10]If we can bring that to
light, it would be a big hit!

\SE[14]In other words, it's an infiltration mission!!
\!\SE[12]We'll directly expose the truth! \.We'll also make
contact with Nikita-san!! \!\SE[11]If we can secure
irrefutable evidence, it'll be a triple crown! \....That's
the plan!!
\SE[90]Well, it does make sense... I wonder?

\SE[14]Then, I'll go...! \SE[13]Nikita is our savior, after
all!

\SE[12]I can really feel the motivation, but... \.There's
still a lack of preparation... \!\SE[38]There are many
uncertainties, and it's difficult to proceed with the
execution...

\SE[4]I understand how you feel, but please calm down a
little. \!\SE[51]Rushing will only ruin things. \!\SE[72]We
have confirmed that she is safe, so let's proceed carefully.

\SE[2]...Oh, that's right. \.There's one thing I forgot to
mention. \!\SE[3]It's about the current residence of Duke
Donyoku....

\SE[2]Former Lira residence \!\SE[0]In other words, it
became the mansion of Miss Elder Sister.

\SE[2]This is confirmed information. Well, I just looked up
the registered address.

\SE[20]So, that person is taking advantage of their position
to surround helpless women... \\SE[21]And behaving in a
filthy manner in my house...?

\SE[57]Y-Yes, that's right.... \.There's a fairly high
probability.... \!\SE[21]\}The house itself was legitimately
purchased, but...

\SE[2]I will infiltrate. \.The departure will be tomorrow.
\.If necessary, I will bring down my social status to hell.
\!\SE[51]Cat. \.You should come with me too.

\SE[4]Oh, we're going tomorrow...!? \SE[17]Didn't you just
say rushing will only ruin things earlier!?

\SE[2]If these two are going, then fine. \!\SE[7]But if I
go, I already know the internal structure and we can skip a
significant portion of the preliminary investigation, right?

\SE[14]I-It seems like it's become tomorrow! \SE[57]I might
ask the stay-behind group for support too... So! \SE[21]I'll
make various preparations...!!

\SE[14]If things get tough, I'll tear them to shreds! Don't
worry! I'll heal you with magic. \SE[2]That's what she said.

\SE[72]I see. \.That's the worst-case scenario, but it's
fine.
